A person's true nature is revealed
not when they're being watched,
but in the heat of battle.

rows.label: qst102109_msg0002

Things didn't quite go as I
expected... but I'm counting
on you for this matter.

rows.label: qst102109_msg0101
rows.name:
The Spike Urchons have attacked
this village before...

rows.label: qst102109_msg0102
rows.name: They know how good human food tastes.

rows.label: qst102109_msg0103
rows.name:
Wipe them out before they
get inside the village!

rows.label: qst102109_msg0202
rows.name:
To disappear at a time like
this... It's just as I feared...
